        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Retirement Parity for Student Loans Act </b><strong>of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill allows certain employer-sponsored retirement plans to make matching contributions for an employee's student loan payments as if the loan payments were salary reduction contributions to the retirement plan.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
